        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[哈尔滨七区实施临时管控]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>因出现一起冠病病例，中国黑龙江省哈尔滨市的七个地区</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>实施了疫情防控临时管控</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>措施</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>，并要求居民在非必要的情况下不要外出。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>这七个地区分别是</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>道里、道外、南岗、香坊、平房、松北，以及呼兰。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>据央视网报道，哈尔滨市指挥部在星期天（8月28日）发布的通知中透露上述消息。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1">
        
</div>


</section>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>通知还说，这七个地区的全部人员，从星期天起至星期二（30日）须参加核酸检测、每天一次，并警告对未按规定时限要求参加核酸检测的人员健康码赋黄码等。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>据黑龙江省卫健委消息，黑龙江省截至星期六（27日）现有本土确诊病例一例，本土无症状感染者51例。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>另一方面，受疫情影响，中国知名歌手张杰原定于星期六在哈尔滨举行的巡演已延期。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<div id="innity-in-post"></div>
<div id="dfp-ad-midarticlespecial">
        
</div>



<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>张杰工作室在微博上说：“具体变更时间将根据相关部门的意见，在官方渠道另行通知。”</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
      


<div class="cx_paywall_placeholder" id="sph_cdp_40"></div>
       ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Sun, 28 Aug 2022 02:14:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/story20220828-1307317</guid>
